<div class="banner container-fluid  mb-3 p-4">
    <img src="~/image/big-banner-0.jpg" class="img-fluid">
</div>


<div class="carousel-bottom carousel slide carousel-fade shadow-lg" data-bs-ride="carousel">
    <div class="carousel-inner">
        <div class="carousel-item active">
            <img src="~/image/last-carousel-1.jpg">
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-item">
            <img src="~/image/last-carousel-2.jpg">
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-item">
            <img src="~/image/last-carousel-3.jpg">
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-item">
            <img src="~/image/last-carousel-4.jpg">
        </div>
    </div>
    <button class="carousel-control-prev" type="button" data-bs-target="carousel-bottom" data-bs-slide="prev">
        <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <span class="visually-hidden">Previous</span>
    </button>
    <button class="carousel-control-next" type="button" data-bs-target="carousel-bottom" data-bs-slide="next">
        <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <span class="visually-hidden">Next</span>
    </button>
</div>


<div class="newsletter container d-flex flex-column align-items-start justify-content-center">
    <h1>NewsLetter</h1>
    <h6>Fique por dentro das novidades, receba descontos exclusivos e muito mais.</h6>
    <div class="d-flex w-100">
        <input type="email" placeholder="Digite o seu email..." class="email w-75 me-1  mb-1 ps-2"  />
        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-dark">Cadastre-se</button>
    </div>
    <div class=" d-flex align-content-center p-0 m-0">
        <input class="checkbox me-2" type="checkbox"/>
        <p class="p-0 m-0">
            Ao se cadastrar você concorda em receber ofertas e novidades da loja DigitalStore por e-mail conforme a <u>Política de Privacidade</u>.
        </p>
    </div>
</div>




